# ── Metadata Source ─────────────────────────────────────────
# You need an OMDb API key for the app to work (free, instant).
# Get yours at: https://www.omdbapi.com/apikey.aspx
# Set this in the app Settings page (not as an env var)

# ── Image Source (optional, for high-res posters/backgrounds) ──
# Fanart.tv API Key
# Get yours at: https://fanart.tv/get-an-api-key/
# Without this, OMDb low-res thumbnails are used for posters.
# No backgrounds will appear (hero banners, detail modals).
# Set this in the app Settings page.

# ── Discovery Lists (recommended, for Trending/Popular/Top-Rated) ──
# Trakt.tv Client ID
# Create an app at: https://trakt.tv/oauth/applications
# Copy the "Client ID" and paste in Settings.
# Without this, OMDb keyword search is used for discovery (less accurate).
# Set this in the app Settings page.
